		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" Rescue the Princess: After I pull the two switches to open the door to the hallway in the final section, I enter the hallway at a slightly crooked angle and I used diagonal inputs to straighten myself out. But this looks a bit slow, so maybe I could enter the hallway at a straighter angle to save time.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" The Trench Run: In the boss fight for this level, I only shot the spaceship with red lasers rather than pink orbs, which deal 2 hearts of damage. The red lasers only deal 1 heart of damage, so I could probably save time by firing pink orbs with red lasers instead of only firing red lasers.
		$LF
	]li
